msgid "5.1.1. Introduction"
msgstr "5-1-1 مقدمة"

#: ../../SO5.md:56
msgid ""
"This indicator aims at capturing the information on international "
"resources provided and/or received through bilateral and multilateral "
"channels for the implementation of the Convention. If the reporting "
"country Party is both a provider and a recipient of international public "
"bilateral and/or multilateral resources, information on both resources "
"provided and received should be reported."
msgstr ""

