"the file to the system. If the default data has been corrected or "
"provided by the Party, the summary data shown will reflect this updated "
"information. Information in the Excel spreadsheet can be reported at any "
"desired level of detail. Otherwise, Parties can reject the default data "
"and manually compile the summary table with aggregated data, as described"
" above under “Validating default data for SO5-1 to SO5-3”."
