msgid ""
"The table shown in the dedicated section in PRAIS4 **includes "
"methodological information for default data**, as explained in the [Good "
"Practice Guidance for SO5](https://www.unccd.int/resources/manuals-and-"
"guides/good-practice-guidance-national-reporting-unccd-strategic-"
